<view class="page home-page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view>
      <text class="eyebrow">linkmai</text>
      <view class="title">交通事故自助处理助手</view>
    </view>
    <view class="hero-mark">LM</view>
  </view>

  <view class="subcopy">
    建档、补材料、测算和文书草稿都围绕一个案件推进。复杂情况会提示人工复核。
  </view>

  <button class="primary-button start-button" bindtap="startCase">
    开始处理事故
  </button>

  <view class="card current-card">
    <view class="card-top">
      <view>
        <view class="section-title">{{currentCase.title}}</view>
        <text class="muted case-plate">{{currentCase.plate}} · {{currentCase.status}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="pill risk-mid">风险 {{currentCase.riskLevel}}</text>
    </view>

    <view class="stage-rail">
      <view wx:for="{{stages}}" wx:key="label" class="stage-item {{item.status}}">
        <view class="stage-dot"></view>
        <text>{{item.label}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="next-box">
      <text class="muted">下一步</text>
      <view class="next-action">{{currentCase.nextAction}}</view>
      <view class="next-meta">
        <text class="muted">{{currentCase.nextActionTime}}</text>
        <text class="pill">缺 {{currentCase.pendingCount}} 项材料</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="progress-track">
      <view class="progress-fill" style="width: {{currentCase.progress}}%;"></view>
    </view>

    <view class="entitlements">
      <text class="muted">已解锁</text>
      <text wx:for="{{currentCase.unlocked}}" wx:key="*this" class="mini-tag">{{item}}</text>
    </view>

    <button class="secondary-button" bindtap="openCase">继续处理</button>
  </view>

  <view class="quick-grid">
    <view
      wx:for="{{quickActions}}"
      wx:key="label"
      class="quick-item card"
      data-path="{{item.path}}"
      bindtap="openQuick"
    >
      <view class="quick-icon">{{index + 1}}</view>
      <text>{{item.label}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="warning-panel notice">
    复杂事故、重伤、酒驾、逃逸等情况将建议人工复核。
  </view>
</view>
